author: Jennifer Fickley-Baker
title: Disney Parks After Dark: Dusk at Disney Springs
text:
Tonight’s “ After Dark ” image was snapped in the new Town Center area of Disney Springs .
In addition to offering an amazing shopping experience at retailers like Zara , Anthropologie , Under Armour Brand House , ALEX & ANI , and many others, Town Center really comes alive at night. It’s a great place to also grab dinner at Homecoming or Frontera Cocina , dessert or a late night snack at Sprinkles .
Tell us, what’s your favorite part of this lovely new area?
